                    <items id="text">Function, daily living</items>
                    <items id="description">Function, daily living
The following questions concern your physical function. By this we mean your ability to move around and to look after yourself. For each of the following activities please indicate the degree of difficulty you have experienced in the last week due to your knee.</items>
                    <items id="comment">Have “Function, daily living” in bold font.
Have “last week” in bold font.</items>
